Package: SpatialExperiment
Type: Package
Title: S4 Class for Spatial Experiments handling 
Version: 0.99.3
Date: 2020-07-21
Authors@R: c(
    person("Dario", "Righelli", role=c("aut", "cre"), 
        email="dario.righelli@gmail.com"),
        person("Davide", "Risso", role=c("aut"), 
        email="risso.davide@gmail.com"))
Description: Defines S4 classes for storing data for spatial experiments.
    Main examples are reported by using seqFISH and 10x-Visium Spatial Gene 
    Expression data. 
    This includes specialized methods for storing, retrieving 
    spatial coordinates, 10x dedicated parameters and their handling.
License: GPL-3
